Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_analysis_summary(25.10)                  report_analysis_summary(25.10)

Name
       report_analysis_summary  -  Generates  timing slack summary reports for
       specified analysis view(s)

Syntax
       report_analysis_summary

       [-help]

       [-csv <string>]

       [-merged_views]

       [-retime {path_slew_propagation | aocv_path_slew_propagation}]

       [-retime_mode {exhaustive}]

       [-view <viewName>]

       [> <filename[.gz]>]

       [>> <filename[.gz]>]

       [-early | -late ]

       [-expanded_summary_clocks | -merged_groups]

       Generates timing slack summary reports for specified analysis  view(s).
       This command categorizes the slack summary in terms of groups - In2reg,
       Reg2reg, Reg2Out, and In2Out. A column "ALL" is displayed that regroups
       in2reg, in2out, reg2reg, and reg2out details.

       By  default,  the slack is categorized in terms of worst negative slack
       (WNS), total negative slack (TNS), and the total number  of  violations
       in group-based mode.

       The report_analysis_summary command is supported in path-based analysis
       (PBA) mode.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       {> | >>} <filename>
              When  specified  with >, writes the report to the specified file
              name. If the file already exists, the software overwrites it.

              When specified with >>, writes the report to the specified  file
              name.  If the file already exists, the software concatenates the
              report to the end of the file.

              Note: To write a compressed report, add the .gzextension to  the
              file name.

              Default:  Report  is  displayed on standard output without being
              saved.

       -csv <string>
              Specifies the name of the CSV output file.

       -early Generates report for hold analysis mode for early paths.

       -expanded_summary_clocks
              Generates report in terms of each  possible  clock  domain  pair
              separately.

       -late  Generates report for setup analysis mode for late paths.

       -merged_groups
              Merges all the clock groups for a consolidated timing summary.

       -merged_views
              Generates merged reports across all the views.

       -retime {path_slew_propagation | aocv_path_slew_propagation}
              Reanalyzes the defined set of paths using the specified method.

              By default, the timing report shows a maximum of 2 million paths
              for retime PBA analysis.

       -retime_mode {exhaustive}
              Reanalyzes the specified set of paths using the specified retime
              mode.

       -view <viewName>
              Generates  report  for the specified analysis views only. By de-
              fault, all the active views are analyzed.

Example
              * The report_analysis_summary command shows the following report
                output:

                REPORT ANALYSIS SUMMARY (View:default_emulate_view) (EL:Setup)

                ===============================================================

                REPORT ANALYSIS SUMMARY (View:default_emulate_view) (EL:Hold)

                ===============================================================

                GroupType:ClockGate

                ==============================================================

                All                IN2REG            IN2OUT            REG2REG
                REG2OUT

                -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                WNS:TNS:#VIO     WNS:TNS:#VIO     WNS:TNS:#VIO    WNS:TNS:#VIO
                WNS:TNS:#VIO   FromClk->ToClk

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                -5.614:-5.614:1  0.000:0.000:0  0.000:0.000:0  -5.614:-5.614:1
                0.000:0.000:0  *->*

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                GroupType:Standard

                ============================================================================================

                All               IN2REG             IN2OUT            REG2REG
                REG2OUT

                ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                WNS:TNS:#VIO      WNS:TNS:#VIO     WNS:TNS:#VIO   WNS:TNS:#VIO
                WNS:TNS:#VIO   FromClk->ToClk

                ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                -8.897:-8.897:1          0.000:0.000:0           0.000:0.000:0
                -8.897:-8.897:1 0.000:0.000:0  *->CLK_W_1

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                -0.571:-0.571:1  -0.571:-0.571:1 0.000:0.000:0   0.000:0.000:0
                0.000:0.000:0  *->CLK_W_2

                --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

